<drama>
	<stage src="opening.cbjstg" x="12" y="7"/>
	<bgm src="aged_forest.ogg" vol="160"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm1" x="4" y="8" dir="r"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm2" x="9" y="10" dir="l"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm3" x="12" y="10" dir="l"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm4" x="16" y="9" dir="l"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm5" x="18" y="9" dir="l"/>
	<put type="Caveman" id="cm6" x="21" y="8" dir="l"/>
	
	<fadein/>
	
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Brothers, Thank you for gathering</en>
		<ja>형제들, 와줘서 고마워</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>As you know, since barbarians came, we have no time to rest</en>
		<ja>모두 알다시피, 야만인들이 침략한 후로, 우린 쉴 틈이 없었어</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>What we need is a new world</en>
		<ja>우리에게 필요한 건 신세계</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm4">
		<en>That's right!</en>
		<ja>옳소!</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Firstly I will scoop barbarians and open the way</en>
		<ja>우선 내가 야만인들을 처리하고 길을 개척해야 해</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Even if I died, continue to open the way</en>
		<ja>설령 내가 죽더라도, 누군가가 계속해서 길을 열어줬으면 해</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm2">
		<en>I understood. After you died I will go next</en>
		<ja>알겠어. 죽으면 내가 그걸 이어 받을게</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm2">
		<en>But, don't die</en>
		<ja>그래도, 죽지는 마</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Of course, that's it</en>
		<ja>물론, 그럴 생각은 없어</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Brothers, Let's live again together</en>
		<ja>그럼, 살아서 다시 만나자고</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm3">
		<en>Wait a minute</en>
		<ja>잠깐</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm3">
		<en>Brothers are caught in various places</en>
		<ja>형제들이 여기저기에 붙잡혀있어</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm3">
		<en>If you release them, they will help us</en>
		<ja>그들을 풀어준다면, 큰 힘이 되어줄 거야</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>I heard good things</en>
		<ja>좋은 걸 들었군</ja>
	</talk>
	<talk sbj="cm1">
		<en>Well then, my brothers, farewells!</en>
		<ja>그럼, 잘 있어, 형제들!</ja>
	</talk>
	<leave sbj="cm1"/>
	<talk sbj="cm3">
		<en>I hope you to survive...</en>
		<ja>무사하기를 빌어...</ja>
	</talk>
	
	<fadeout/>
</drama>